</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
     FAQ ACCORDION
════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="faq-section">
  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-grid">
      <div class="faq-col">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            What is MHT-CET Counselling? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a">MHT-CET Counselling is the official admission process for engineering colleges in Maharashtra. Our platform helps you navigate it with expert support, cutoff data, and personalised college lists.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            How accurate are the college predictions? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a">Our predictions are based on 5+ years of historical cutoff data and are updated after every CAP round. Accuracy depends on category, branch, and location preferences.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            Will I get personal counselling? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a">Yes! Every paid plan includes one-on-one expert counselling sessions. The Pro and Premium plans include multiple calls with dedicated counsellors.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            How do I start? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a">Simply click "Get College Suggestions", choose a plan that fits your needs, fill in your basic details, and complete payment. You'll get access to your personalised report instantly.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-col">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            Is my data safe with MHT-CET Counselling? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a">Absolutely. We use industry-standard 256-bit SSL encryption. Your data is never shared with third parties without consent. See our Privacy Policy for details.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            Which data is used for predictions? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a">We use official DTE Maharashtra CAP round data, MHTCET merit lists, seat matrices, and historical admission records spanning 5+ years.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            Do you help with CAP choice filling? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a">Yes — our Pro and Premium plans include hands-on assistance with CAP choice filling, option form strategy, and document verification guidance.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            Can I get refund if I'm not satisfied? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-a">We offer a full refund within 24 hours of payment if no counselling session has been conducted. See our <a href="/terms" style="color:var(--blue2);">Terms & Conditions</a> for full refund policy.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

